<style>
  /* ===== Bespoke: AI Advantage Section (Dark Luxury) ===== */
  .bmx-ai-advantage {
    --ink: #f5f5f5;
    --muted: #a0a0a0;
    --paper: #252525;
    --accent: #D4AF37;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage h2 {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 34px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .divider {
    width: 96px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .column {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 44px 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: box-shadow .3s ease, background .3s ease, border-color .3s ease;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .column:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    background: #2a2a2a;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .icon-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    fill: none;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .column-title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 22px;
  }

  .bmx-ai-advantage .column-text {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  @media(max-width: 900px){
    .bmx-ai-advantage .columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="bmx-ai-advantage" aria-labelledby="bm-ai-title">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 id="bm-ai-title">Human Artistry. Unconstrained Production.</h2>
    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="columns">
      <!-- Column 1: The Human Element -->
      <div class="column">
        <div class="icon-row">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="column-title">The Human Element</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="column-text">
          I write every lyric and melody personally. A machine cannot understand your partner's inside jokes, the specific ache of a memory, or the story of how you met. That part remains 100% human.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2: The AI Advantage -->
      <div class="column">
        <div class="icon-row">
          <div class="icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="column-title">The AI Advantage</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="column-text">
          Traditional orchestral production requires booking musicians, engineers, and studio spaceâ€”a process that takes weeks of coordination. By utilizing advanced AI instrumentation, I can orchestrate your song immediately after writing it. We eliminate the logistical delays of the studio, delivering a full symphonic arrangement on the timeline you actually need.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

